[
  {
    "startTime": 0.9,
    "endTime": 1.32,
    "text": "So I have not seen you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.32,
    "endTime": 2.2190000000000003,
    "text": "Well, I saw you--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.219,
    "endTime": 3.51,
    "text": "I ran into you at a restaurant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.51,
    "endTime": 5.55,
    "text": "But I haven't really congratulated you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.55,
    "endTime": 7.199,
    "text": "because the last time you were here,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.2,
    "endTime": 8.7,
    "text": "it was before award season."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.7,
    "endTime": 10.469,
    "text": "And you've won just about every award"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.47,
    "endTime": 13.55,
    "text": "that there was to win for Big Little Lies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.55,
    "endTime": 13.846,
    "text": "So congratulations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.846,
    "endTime": 15.29,
    "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.29,
    "endTime": 15.79,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.79,
    "endTime": 17.247,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.248,
    "endTime": 22.900000000000002,
    "text": "Yeah, that was an amazing, amazing journey with that show."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.9,
    "endTime": 23.849999999999998,
    "text": "And it ain't over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.85,
    "endTime": 28.55,
    "text": "No, because it's-- look, we can't wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.55,
    "endTime": 33.910000000000004,
    "text": "And Meryl Streep joined the cast, which that's--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.91,
    "endTime": 35.937999999999995,
    "text": "Yeah, we got lucky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.939,
    "endTime": 36.48,
    "text": "I mean, she--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.48,
    "endTime": 36.986,
    "text": "Not lucky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.987,
    "endTime": 38.82,
    "text": "Who wouldn't want to be a part of that cast?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.82,
    "endTime": 40.2,
    "text": "Of course, she'd want to do that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.2,
    "endTime": 41.970000000000006,
    "text": "But she signed on without having read"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.97,
    "endTime": 45.36,
    "text": "any script, which is a big support of us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.36,
    "endTime": 46.589,
    "text": "as a group of women."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.59,
    "endTime": 49.45,
    "text": "She was like I want to be in the coven,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.45,
    "endTime": 52.910000000000004,
    "text": "she said, [LAUGHTER] which I thought was funny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.91,
    "endTime": 54.589999999999996,
    "text": "Yeah, she's fantastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.6,
    "endTime": 56.160000000000004,
    "text": "And she's definitely in it now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.16,
    "endTime": 61.778999999999996,
    "text": "She's-- and she plays Perry, who was my husband in Big Little"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.78,
    "endTime": 62.28,
    "text": "Lies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.28,
    "endTime": 63.96,
    "text": "And for anyone that hasn't seen it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.96,
    "endTime": 68.4,
    "text": "she plays his mother, who comes back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.4,
    "endTime": 70.5,
    "text": "That's how the show begins--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.5,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "comes to live with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 74.36,
    "text": "So we find out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.36,
    "endTime": 75.47,
    "text": "Wow, she's the--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.47,
    "endTime": 77.7,
    "text": "Mother-in-law living with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.7,
    "endTime": 78.66,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.66,
    "endTime": 82.289,
    "text": "That would explain a lot of things that you think, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.29,
    "endTime": 82.79,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.79,
    "endTime": 83.91000000000001,
    "text": "Is that what that is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.91,
    "endTime": 85.85,
    "text": "It will be unraveled."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.85,
    "endTime": 86.46,
    "text": "You'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.46,
    "endTime": 87.8,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.8,
    "endTime": 87.58,
    "text": "No more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.58,
    "endTime": 88.98,
    "text": "I can tell you no more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.98,
    "endTime": 91.5,
    "text": "I think I've already said too much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.5,
    "endTime": 91.619,
    "text": "Not really."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.62,
    "endTime": 92.28,
    "text": "That's my problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.28,
    "endTime": 94.53,
    "text": "No, she's the mother-in-law and she's living with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.53,
    "endTime": 96.24,
    "text": "I think that's not saying anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.24,
    "endTime": 97.259,
    "text": "Is she evil?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.26,
    "endTime": 98.56,
    "text": "Is she--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.56,
    "endTime": 99.81,
    "text": "No more, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.81,
    "endTime": 101.5,
    "text": "No more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.5,
    "endTime": 102.52,
    "text": "Isn't that hard, though?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.52,
    "endTime": 103.17999999999999,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.19,
    "endTime": 104.5,
    "text": "Like you have all this information,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.5,
    "endTime": 106.416,
    "text": "and you have like a couple of glasses of wine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.416,
    "endTime": 107.58,
    "text": "And you're out somewhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.58,
    "endTime": 109.78,
    "text": "And you're like-- yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.78,
    "endTime": 111.67,
    "text": "Do you worry about that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.67,
    "endTime": 114.76,
    "text": "No because I'm quite good at just--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.76,
    "endTime": 116.99000000000001,
    "text": "I mean, obviously, I'm a producer on the series."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.99,
    "endTime": 119.559,
    "text": "So I'm the one who's going shhh, shhh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.56,
    "endTime": 120.95,
    "text": "Everyone has to be on lock down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.95,
    "endTime": 121.908,
    "text": "Who do you worry about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.908,
    "endTime": 124.63,
    "text": "Who has the big mouth?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.63,
    "endTime": 125.786,
    "text": "Reese, probably."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.786,
    "endTime": 126.59400000000001,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.594,
    "endTime": 127.94,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.94,
    "endTime": 129.69,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm sure it's Reese."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.69,
    "endTime": 132.48,
    "text": "No, probably the two of us have a bit of a big mouth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.48,
    "endTime": 133.82,
    "text": "So we have to watch it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.82,
    "endTime": 135.57899999999998,
    "text": "But please, just--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.58,
    "endTime": 138.3,
    "text": "No, no, Reese-- I know her well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.3,
    "endTime": 139.966,
    "text": "No she doesn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.966,
    "endTime": 141.9,
    "text": "She's-- and I'm trying to--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.9,
    "endTime": 142.423,
    "text": "She's a very good secret keeper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.423,
    "endTime": 143.82,
    "text": "Well, she's told me some things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.82,
    "endTime": 145.79,
    "text": "And I'm trying to keep it a secret."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.8,
    "endTime": 145.44,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.44,
    "endTime": 147.3,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm not going to tell you because I'm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.3,
    "endTime": 148.3,
    "text": "good at keeping secrets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.3,
    "endTime": 153.63000000000002,
    "text": "But she's told me the entire plot line for this next season."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.63,
    "endTime": 156.525,
    "text": "I think I've told my husband the entire plot line."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.526,
    "endTime": 157.65,
    "text": "Well, he has ti know stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.65,
    "endTime": 158.68,
    "text": "But you're allowed to do that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.68,
    "endTime": 159.18,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.18,
    "endTime": 162.27,
    "text": "Except he doesn't know the Aquaman story line."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.27,
    "endTime": 163.282,
    "text": "Yes, now you're kids--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.282,
    "endTime": 164.74,
    "text": "Because they're on even bigger lock"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.74,
    "endTime": 167.5,
    "text": "down those comic book films--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.5,
    "endTime": 167.55,
    "text": "I bet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.55,
    "endTime": 168.425,
    "text": "--are like oh my god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.425,
    "endTime": 170.79000000000002,
    "text": "You're kids must be freaking out that you're in that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.79,
    "endTime": 172.95,
    "text": "Yes, that's the only thing that gives me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.95,
    "endTime": 174.73399999999998,
    "text": "any credibility with them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.735,
    "endTime": 176.4,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.4,
    "endTime": 177.17000000000002,
    "text": "That's the only thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.17,
    "endTime": 178.559,
    "text": "Yeah, because--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.56,
    "endTime": 179.7,
    "text": "In terms of my career."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.7,
    "endTime": 181.38,
    "text": "Right, because they can't watch Big Little Lies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.38,
    "endTime": 183.15,
    "text": "They don't know how great you are in that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.15,
    "endTime": 184.44,
    "text": "because they're too young."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.44,
    "endTime": 188.829,
    "text": "Yes, but they were in as extras in Big Little Lies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.83,
    "endTime": 189.33,
    "text": "Oh, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.33,
    "endTime": 190.747,
    "text": "Yes, which I've never told anyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.747,
    "endTime": 191.371,
    "text": "In this season?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.371,
    "endTime": 192.876,
    "text": "Here I am now being a big mouth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.876,
    "endTime": 193.87,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.87,
    "endTime": 195.19,
    "text": "In this season or last season?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.19,
    "endTime": 195.69,
    "text": "Coming up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.69,
    "endTime": 196.3,
    "text": "Coming up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.3,
    "endTime": 196.8,
    "text": "I have--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.8,
    "endTime": 198.8,
    "text": "Ask me about my cats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.8,
    "endTime": 198.58,
    "text": "OK, I will."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.58,
    "endTime": 199.43,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.43,
    "endTime": 200.99,
    "text": "By the way, I still have those--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.99,
    "endTime": 202.5,
    "text": "the art that they made for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.5,
    "endTime": 203.4,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.4,
    "endTime": 204.179,
    "text": "It's in my dressing room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.179,
    "endTime": 204.97,
    "text": "I still have those."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.97,
    "endTime": 205.68,
    "text": "It was really sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.68,
    "endTime": 206.4,
    "text": "Isn't that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.4,
    "endTime": 206.53900000000002,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.539,
    "endTime": 208.14,
    "text": "And they love you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.14,
    "endTime": 209.488,
    "text": "And they want to be on the show."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.489,
    "endTime": 210.78,
    "text": "Well, then they should be here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.78,
    "endTime": 211.78,
    "text": "No, they're not allowed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.78,
    "endTime": 212.325,
    "text": "Why not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.325,
    "endTime": 213.72,
    "text": "Because--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.72,
    "endTime": 216.87,
    "text": "All right, let's talk about the cats because you just started--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.87,
    "endTime": 218.70000000000002,
    "text": "you joined Instagram, finally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.7,
    "endTime": 219.82,
    "text": "Welcome aboard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.82,
    "endTime": 220.56,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.56,
    "endTime": 221.207,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.207,
    "endTime": 222.4,
    "text": "Why did you decide--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.4,
    "endTime": 222.70600000000002,
    "text": "Took me a while."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.706,
    "endTime": 224.13,
    "text": "Why did you decide to start?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.13,
    "endTime": 226.39,
    "text": "Because it's a lovely contact with people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.39,
    "endTime": 226.89,
    "text": "Yes, it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.89,
    "endTime": 227.89899999999997,
    "text": "It's actually very direct."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.9,
    "endTime": 228.399,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.399,
    "endTime": 233.29,
    "text": "And it's very-- and it's nice to show a little bit of your life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.29,
    "endTime": 235.864,
    "text": "And I just think it's a nice way to connect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.864,
    "endTime": 237.78,
    "text": "And there's some funny, funny things on there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.78,
    "endTime": 238.78,
    "text": "You're showing your cats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.78,
    "endTime": 239.53,
    "text": "You have two cats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.53,
    "endTime": 240.47,
    "text": "I'm that person that--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.47,
    "endTime": 240.97,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.97,
    "endTime": 242.3,
    "text": "--shows my animal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.3,
    "endTime": 243.85000000000002,
    "text": "How-- what are their names?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.85,
    "endTime": 245.34,
    "text": "Ginger and Snow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.34,
    "endTime": 246.38400000000001,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.384,
    "endTime": 248.48999999999998,
    "text": "I'm going to guess the white one's Snow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.5,
    "endTime": 249.62,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.62,
    "endTime": 250.20000000000002,
    "text": "Wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.2,
    "endTime": 251.173,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.174,
    "endTime": 252.15,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.15,
    "endTime": 254.75,
    "text": "That would be amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.75,
    "endTime": 255.369,
    "text": "All right, so Ginger and Snow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.37,
    "endTime": 255.87,
    "text": "And--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.87,
    "endTime": 256.579,
    "text": "Sisters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.579,
    "endTime": 256.834,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.834,
    "endTime": 257.5,
    "text": "They're sisters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.5,
    "endTime": 259.41,
    "text": "They're from the same litter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.41,
    "endTime": 261.77900000000005,
    "text": "So-- Anyways, [INAUDIBLE]."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.779,
    "endTime": 262.83,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.83,
    "endTime": 265.361,
    "text": "Wow, so--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.362,
    "endTime": 267.57000000000005,
    "text": "I can't believe you're not showing the belly, though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.57,
    "endTime": 268.469,
    "text": "The one with her belly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.47,
    "endTime": 269.511,
    "text": "There's one with a belly?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.511,
    "endTime": 270.51000000000005,
    "text": "[INAUDIBLE] her belly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.51,
    "endTime": 270.849,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.85,
    "endTime": 273.11,
    "text": "Which is the highest form of trust of an animal, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.11,
    "endTime": 273.61,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.61,
    "endTime": 275.331,
    "text": "[CROWD AWING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.331,
    "endTime": 275.83000000000004,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.83,
    "endTime": 276.599,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.6,
    "endTime": 278.16,
    "text": "That's a great picture, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.16,
    "endTime": 280.61,
    "text": "Is this cat gorgeous or what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.61,
    "endTime": 281.29200000000003,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.292,
    "endTime": 283.59,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.6,
    "endTime": 285.57500000000005,
